Maj-id is a talented kick boxer from a gray, anonymous suburb in The Netherlands. 
As his fighting prowess brings him increasing notoriety in-and outside the ring, 
the worlds of kickboxing and organized crime begin to blur into each another and 
Maj id begins to lose sight of what it is he really wants.
